### Find All books
GET http://localhost:8080/book
Accept: application/json

### Find All Books with min pages equals
GET http://localhost:8080/books/min-pages/2300
Accept: application/json

### Create Book
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "pages": 431,
  "year": 2008
}

### Update Book
@id = 6a3313c2152e7e9df3709787
PUT http://localhost:8080/books/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code - Updated",
  "pages": 464,
  "year": 2008
}

### Delete Book
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/{{id}}

### [POOL TEST] Slow endpoint — fire 3x simultaneously to exhaust pool (maxSize=2)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/slow
Accept: application/json